{"tid":2417755,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男教師涉非禮校內三男生 官不信涉權鬥誣告 罪成還柙候判","createTime":"2021-02-22T06:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T10:48:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48a6259d67798101938a9682d8c433bba4892a61","tid":2417755,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"九龍區某中學35歲男教師，被指3年內5度侵犯校內3名中三至中四男生，包括伸手入男生校服內「撩」肚臍皮膚和毛髮並說「你好多毛」，又試過伸手入男生衫內打圈摸乳頭，並以下體壓向男生背部、摸大腿和索抱。男教師被控五項非禮罪，辯方聆訊期間指出案中三名男生遭與被告關係欠佳的教師利用，從而誣告被告。法官今裁決時不接納辯方說法，直指若如此便需要編劇、綵排及演練，甚至會冒上妨礙司法公正的風險，裁定被告其中兩項非禮罪成，還柙至下月15日判刑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/HYTLE2GLNNBRHFUTFWXXRFKHSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FHYTLE2GLNNBRHFUTFWXXRFKHSM%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYwZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=167ba42d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FHYTLE2GLNNBRHFUTFWXXRFKHSM%2F&h=63dd20f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/HYTLE2GLNNBRHFUTFWXXRFKHSM/</a>"},{"pid":"c44feed761c5b4866a5352dfebccc0d500e4fb0f","tid":2417755,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dO1oRSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdO1oRSo.jpg&h=e9677130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyGj9FT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyGj9FT.gif&h=a00b6c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/CxnCWkQ.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxnCWkQ.gif&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYwZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=ad55b5a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/CxnCWkQ.gif</a>"},{"pid":"cd68f4df78aa294dd7f099004f9d3a83d9ae00c4","tid":2417755,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi